            "pub_date": "2025-02-13 14:55:31",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "日股收市漲1.28%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">日股午後續於高位徘徊，日經平均指數全日穩企於39000點之上，收報39461點，升497點或1.28%。</p>\n</div>",
